Class LocalCSVDataSource

  • java.lang.Object
    • stocks.CSVSources
      • stocks.LocalCSVDataSource
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    StockDataSource
    public class LocalCSVDataSource
extends CSVSources
    The LocalCSVDataSource class represents a CSV stock data source from a local file. This allows the program to download API data to use locally in the future or for the user to add their own CSV file. IMPORTANT: If using your own file, you must put the csv file in the stockdata directory.
